                <h1>Explore the Legacy: GM Heritage Center</h1>
                <p>The GM Heritage Center is a celebrated museum showcasing the rich history of General Motors and the automotive industry. Located in Michigan, it features a stunning collection of vintage cars, interactive exhibits, and historical artifacts. Visitors can explore the evolution of GM's innovation and design, making it a must-see for auto enthusiasts and history buffs alike.</p>
